<p><strong><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="2" color="#FBB202"><a name="$newstime">Yet another site update</a></font> </strong><small><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="1" color="#000000">Posted Sunday, July 4 23:21 by <a href="mailto:kornel@linux3d.net">kornel</a></font></small><br> <font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="2" color="#000000">Ok, just to let you know that I finished with the installation and configuration of the script for the drivers database. It is now integrated into the hardware section's layout.<br>I still need to do some minor tweaks like the bottom page search forms are not yet outputing results. However the search from the menu is working just fine. Some text output needs to be formated with the Lucida font, however I am working on a nice css file.<br><br>Anyway, enjoy. Data will be be added during the coming week. If you know of accelerated drivers for a particular card, please send in info.</font></p>

